Comment: 0,0:00:00.02,0:00:05.02,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 10,0:00:15.01,0:00:19.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Fujimaki! If you keep swinging in the same direction, you'll get dizzy!
Dialogue: 10,0:00:23.75,0:00:25.02,Default,,0,0,0,,He's right, Shun!
Dialogue: 10,0:00:25.49,0:00:29.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if I try to jump, \NI can't let go!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:10.86,0:02:12.06,Thought,,0,0,0,,My hands...
Dialogue: 10,0:02:12.69,0:02:14.13,Thought,,0,0,0,,My hands just won't let go!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:15.15,0:02:17.97,Default,,0,0,0,,What did you say? You can't let go?
Dialogue: 10,0:02:17.97,0:02:19.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Shun-kun...
Dialogue: 10,0:02:19.64,0:02:24.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I've tried to jump time and time again, \Nbut my hands just won't listen, no matter what I do.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:24.77,0:02:26.18,Default,,0,0,0,,What the hell?
Dialogue: 10,0:02:26.18,0:02:27.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Your hands won't listen?
Dialogue: 10,0:02:27.68,0:02:29.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Why won't they listen? How come?
Dialogue: 10,0:02:30.68,0:02:34.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I don't know, but when I try to let go of the high bar,
Dialogue: 10,0:02:35.35,0:02:37.62,Default,,0,0,0,,my hands just won't listen to what I say.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:37.62,0:02:41.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Look, you didn't kill some living being \Nwhile you were a kid, did you?
Dialogue: 10,0:02:41.36,0:02:41.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:02:42.32,0:02:48.73,Default,,0,0,0,,What if the spirit of a slain creature possessed you \Nand made you unable to control your hands?
Dialogue: 10,0:02:51.10,0:02:53.80,Default,,0,0,0,,You’re in big trouble \Nif it’s not exorcised, buddy!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:53.80,0:02:55.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Amen...
Dialogue: 10,0:02:55.60,0:02:57.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, you! Enough with it!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:57.57,0:03:02.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Shun, what exactly happened to you \Nat that training camp?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:09.99,0:03:14.21,Default,,0,0,0,,You think something in him changed\N at the training camp?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:14.21,0:03:20.73,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right. It seems to me, something happened there that gave him a mental shock.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:20.73,0:03:22.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Actually, on his first day...
Dialogue: 10,0:03:22.15,0:03:24.12,Default,,0,0,0,,What did you say?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:28.80,0:03:30.97,Default,,0,0,0,,He punched a hole in the ceiling?!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:30.97,0:03:32.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. That surprised everyone.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:33.34,0:03:37.67,Default,,0,0,0,,While trying to learn a triple somersault on the high bar, he jumped too high
Dialogue: 10,0:03:37.67,0:03:39.80,Default,,0,0,0,,and crashed through the ceiling.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:40.87,0:03:44.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Did he then crash into the bar?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:44.15,0:03:48.81,Default,,0,0,0,,No, he just fell into the pit as he was supposed to, \Nhe didn't meet the bar on his way back.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:48.81,0:03:52.83,Default,,0,0,0,,That's strange. \NIf he didn't even hit the bar...
Dialogue: 10,0:03:52.83,0:03:53.86,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:53.86,0:03:58.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't like it. \NThere used to be an Olympic athlete once.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:58.37,0:04:02.29,Default,,0,0,0,,During practice, \Nhe fell right onto the high bar,
Dialogue: 10,0:04:02.34,0:04:08.48,Default,,0,0,0,,and since then, he's been unable let go of the bar, \Neven while performing a giant swing.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:08.48,0:04:12.46,Default,,0,0,0,,But if Shun didn't even hit the bar...
Dialogue: 10,0:04:12.46,0:04:17.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Come to think of it, Director Sotoyama \Nalso mentioned something similar back then.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:17.09,0:04:21.72,Default,,0,0,0,,He told them about an athlete who failed to clear the bar, landed on it shin-first,
Dialogue: 10,0:04:21.72,0:04:24.91,Default,,0,0,0,,suffered an open fracture, and had bones sticking out...
Dialogue: 10,0:04:24.91,0:04:26.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-What?!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:26.88,0:04:31.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, it was then. That's when Fujimaki-kun started acting strange.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:31.73,0:04:33.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Then that's the reason!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:33.14,0:04:33.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:33.82,0:04:38.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Shun convinced himself that he would suffer the same fate!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:38.24,0:04:42.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Even though his mind wants to let go, \Nhis body rebels!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:42.31,0:04:44.95,Default,,0,0,0,,If so, we're in a bit of a pickle.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:44.95,0:04:48.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah... This problem lies in a mental plane.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:48.52,0:04:53.31,Default,,0,0,0,,If we act carelessly, we'll make it worse than if he actually hit the bar. Worst case scenario...
Dialogue: 10,0:04:53.31,0:04:56.39,Default,,0,0,0,,It might affect his future \Ngymnastics career, correct?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:56.39,0:04:59.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes... We have to do something!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:05.57,0:05:08.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Fujimaki-kun, can you land with a triple somersault now?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:08.87,0:05:10.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I can.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:10.54,0:05:12.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! Show me, show me!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:12.74,0:05:13.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:19.50,0:05:20.80,Default,,0,0,0,,And now!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:25.85,0:05:26.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Footprints...
Dialogue: 10,0:05:26.64,0:05:28.38,Default,,0,0,0,,on the ceiling?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:28.38,0:05:32.59,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no ceiling. \NWe're in Madam's yard!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:35.46,0:05:36.90,Thought,,0,0,0,,Crap!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:37.55,0:05:38.89,Thought,,0,0,0,,High bar...
Dialogue: 10,0:05:59.12,0:06:00.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Just a dream?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:01.72,0:06:03.46,Default,,0,0,0,,That was scary...
Dialogue: 10,0:06:07.33,0:06:11.82,Default,,0,0,0,,There, you're getting sleepy. \NYou want to sleep.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:11.82,0:06:15.63,Default,,0,0,0,,You feel more and more sleepy...
Dialogue: 10,0:06:15.63,0:06:18.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, what can you see?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:18.54,0:06:21.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't see anything, \Nmy eyes are closed.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:21.06,0:06:23.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Can't argue with that!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:23.68,0:06:25.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Fujimaki's leading! {https://jisho.org/word/%E6%8A%80%E3%81%82%E3%82%8A - no clue what he means}
Dialogue: 10,0:06:25.28,0:06:27.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up! You're distracting us!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:27.62,0:06:29.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Fujimaki! You need to take it seriously too!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:29.76,0:06:31.55,Default,,0,0,0,,But I'm not messing with you!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:31.55,0:06:35.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Uchida, do you really think you can fix it with hypnosis?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:35.25,0:06:37.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Please leave it to me.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:37.02,0:06:40.76,Default,,0,0,0,,All we need to do is blow his fears away with self-suggestion.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:40.76,0:06:42.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen, Fujimaki.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:42.50,0:06:44.23,Default,,0,0,0,,O-Okay...
Dialogue: 10,0:06:44.23,0:06:47.67,Default,,0,0,0,,You are a bird. A bird.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:47.67,0:06:50.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Since you're a bird, you can fly.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:50.17,0:06:54.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Since you're a bird, you're not afraid of flying. Not afraid.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:56.34,0:06:58.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you hear? "A bird!"
Dialogue: 10,0:06:58.11,0:07:00.84,Default,,0,0,0,,What are gonna do if you \Nturn him into a chicken?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:02.48,0:07:05.09,Default,,0,0,0,,That's it! Your fear is gone!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:05.09,0:07:08.06,Default,,0,0,0,,You're not afraid of the high bar. \NNot one bit afraid!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:08.06,0:07:09.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I-Is that true?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:18.46,0:07:21.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Uchida-senpai, are you sure it worked?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:21.62,0:07:24.84,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll know when you see it. \NOkay, Fujimaki!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:24.84,0:07:27.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Now that you're a bird, you can fly! \NI know you can!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:28.44,0:07:30.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Good luck, Fujimaki-kun!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:30.13,0:07:32.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay! Let go!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:33.35,0:07:34.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Let go, you hear?!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:34.95,0:07:36.32,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:36.32,0:07:39.86,Default,,0,0,0,,You're a bird! A bird! \NDidn't I tell you you're a bird now?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:39.86,0:07:41.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Fly!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:42.56,0:07:44.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Seriously, dude!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:46.03,0:07:47.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Fujimaki-kun!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:52.96,0:07:55.66,Default,,0,0,0,,One-two... fly!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:59.13,0:08:00.64,Default,,0,0,0,,One-two...
Dialogue: 10,0:08:00.64,0:08:03.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Fujimaki! Take a break now.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:10.69,0:08:11.61,Thought,,0,0,0,,What a pain...
Dialogue: 10,0:08:12.34,0:08:16.58,Thought,,0,0,0,,To think a triple somersault from the training camp would backfire at us like that...
Dialogue: 10,0:08:16.58,0:08:19.13,Default,,0,0,0,,What are we gonna do now? What to do?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:19.13,0:08:21.23,Default,,0,0,0,,He was supposed to turn into a bird...
Dialogue: 10,0:08:21.23,0:08:22.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Enough about that.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:22.56,0:08:27.03,Thought,,0,0,0,,The more people around you try to help you, \Nthe deeper your trauma progresses.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:27.03,0:08:32.50,Thought,,0,0,0,,I understand how everyone feels, but that's not enough. \NYou have to overcome it on your own...
Dialogue: 10,0:08:32.50,0:08:37.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Shun! You will practice privately with me \Nearly in the morning starting tomorrow.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:37.21,0:08:38.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Got it?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:40.35,0:08:41.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes...
Dialogue: 10,0:08:50.02,0:08:52.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Madam, you want me to exercise in rain boots?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:53.53,0:08:54.83,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not for that.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:54.83,0:08:57.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I want you to help me dig potatoes.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:57.57,0:08:58.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Potatoes?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:58.79,0:09:02.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Shun, I don't understand the reason for your condition,
Dialogue: 10,0:09:02.37,0:09:05.37,Default,,0,0,0,,but forgetting about the bar for a while would do you good. {unsure}
Dialogue: 10,0:09:05.37,0:09:07.74,Default,,0,0,0,,But I have to practice...
Dialogue: 10,0:09:07.74,0:09:08.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm...
Dialogue: 10,0:09:08.73,0:09:12.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Whatever. If you don't worry, it'll heal soon.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:12.70,0:09:16.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Just don't push yourself too hard for now.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:18.85,0:09:22.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Let Fujimaki-kun stay away from the high bar for a while?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:22.62,0:09:28.62,Default,,0,0,0,,If we let him rest for a while, his fear will subside and he'll return to the high bar in due course.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:28.62,0:09:31.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Until then, we just have to wait.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:32.97,0:09:35.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I also agree with Madam's opinion.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:35.64,0:09:39.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I feel that if we force him to practice, \Nit will only deepen his fear.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:39.56,0:09:44.88,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right. In contrast with our idiotic Trio of Second-years, Shun takes himself too seriously. {refers to Sanada, Uchida, Higashi}
Dialogue: 10,0:09:44.88,0:09:47.38,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what made his condition so severe.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:47.82,0:09:52.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I wish Mari-chan was was still here, \Nso we could force those two on a date.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:52.86,0:09:56.06,Default,,0,0,0,,That'd make for a nice change of pace \Nthat Shun needs so much.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:56.06,0:09:58.92,Default,,0,0,0,,So you made him plant potatoes \Nfor a change of pace... {unsure here and in the next lines}
Dialogue: 10,0:09:58.92,0:10:02.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh I'm sorry, but you'll turn into an old hag yourself in no time. {not sure, she probably understood eri's comment as "planting potatoes is an elderly avocation" so she retorts with "you'll do it yourself soon?"}
Dialogue: 10,0:10:02.56,0:10:03.57,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:03.57,0:10:05.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll give it a try.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:05.04,0:10:05.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:05.77,0:10:09.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want Shun-kun to lose his future \Nover something like this.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:09.74,0:10:12.70,Default,,0,0,0,,So I... I'll do it myself...
Dialogue: 10,0:10:14.48,0:10:17.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I suppose you're right. \NA young one would work better...
Dialogue: 10,0:10:17.88,0:10:19.18,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean? {/Grandma...}
Dialogue: 10,0:10:19.61,0:10:22.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I've planned a trip \Nto the vegetables market tomorrow. {lit: gathering edible wild plants - I don't see a way to explain it in a concise way in english, so I just made it something else old grandmas typically do}
Dialogue: 10,0:10:22.75,0:10:24.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Young one would work better, Grandma.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:36.60,0:10:37.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Shun-kun!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:38.63,0:10:40.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Shun-kun...
Dialogue: 10,0:10:41.70,0:10:43.73,Default,,0,0,0,,This way, Shun-kun!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:46.84,0:10:49.41,Default,,0,0,0,,R-Reiko-senpai is calling you...
Dialogue: 10,0:10:49.41,0:10:50.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:50.01,0:10:51.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm here, Shun-kun.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:53.82,0:10:55.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-What's the matter, Reiko-senpai?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:55.74,0:10:58.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Shun-kun, are you free tomorrow?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:58.02,0:11:01.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh? Well, I have some free time...
Dialogue: 10,0:11:02.46,0:11:05.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go on a date tomorrow.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:06.32,0:11:07.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Date?!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:07.98,0:11:09.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Da— {unsure}
Dialogue: 10,0:11:09.92,0:11:11.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, a date.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:11.30,0:11:12.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Wha...
Dialogue: 10,0:11:12.30,0:11:13.62,Default,,0,0,0,,What the...
Dialogue: 10,0:11:13.62,0:11:15.56,Default,,0,0,0,,O-Orikasa?!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:15.56,0:11:20.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I have two tickets to the amusement park. \NI wanted to go there with you.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:20.96,0:11:21.53,Default,,0,0,0,,U-Um...
Dialogue: 10,0:11:21.80,0:11:23.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Please!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:23.87,0:11:25.58,Default,,0,0,0,,O-Okay...
Dialogue: 10,0:11:26.00,0:11:27.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Say what?!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:27.87,0:11:31.39,Default,,0,0,0,,R-Reiko-senpai and F-Fujimaki-kun?!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:31.39,0:11:32.94,Default,,0,0,0,,On a date?!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:33.49,0:11:36.32,Default,,0,0,0,,This is so wrong! {no clue}
Dialogue: 10,0:11:48.97,0:11:54.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Reiko-sama, why... \NWhy does it have to be Fujimaki of all people?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:55.38,0:12:00.18,Default,,0,0,0,,She looks great in a leotard, but Reiko-senpai in a miniskirt is simply irresistible!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:00.18,0:12:02.12,Default,,0,0,0,,She makes my muscles dance!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:02.12,0:12:07.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Guys, Reiko-senpai's beautiful legs will get dirty from your lascivious looks alone! {unsure}
Dialogue: 10,0:12:07.56,0:12:11.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, are we really following them even inside the amusement park?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:11.18,0:12:12.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:12.33,0:12:16.06,Default,,0,0,0,,As his mentors, we're responsible \Nfor the actions of our disciple.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:16.06,0:12:20.14,Default,,0,0,0,,We must watch him closely to prevent any unacceptable behavior toward Reiko-senpai.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:20.14,0:12:22.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I also must do that, as his classmate.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:23.24,0:12:25.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Ueno, not you too...
Dialogue: 10,0:12:25.36,0:12:28.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! Fujimaki-kun is here!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:29.88,0:12:31.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry to keep you waiting.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:31.15,0:12:33.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Not at all. It's all fine, Shun-kun.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:33.50,0:12:35.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, shall we go?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:36.22,0:12:37.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:37.44,0:12:41.19,Default,,0,0,0,,He even has the nerve \Nto make Reiko-senpai wait!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:41.19,0:12:42.70,Default,,0,0,0,,We must teach him a lesson! {no clue}
Dialogue: 10,0:12:42.70,0:12:43.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm so jealous...
Dialogue: 10,0:12:45.16,0:12:47.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I wanna go on a date too!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:47.08,0:12:50.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I've never been on a date like this in my life!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:50.46,0:12:51.80,Default,,0,0,0,,O-Orikasa...
Dialogue: 10,0:12:51.80,0:12:53.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry to keep you waiting!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:54.67,0:12:57.56,Default,,0,0,0,,You boys are going on a date with me.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:06.34,0:13:09.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Shun desperately needs \Na change of pace right now.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:09.31,0:13:14.36,Default,,0,0,0,,But there can't be a change of pace if you keep hanging around and getting in his way!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:14.36,0:13:17.86,Default,,0,0,0,,As his mentors, you need \Nto be more considerate than that!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:17.86,0:13:20.03,Default,,0,0,0,,B-But that doesn't explain... {unsure, maybe "that's why we were there", I think this and the next 2 lines are one sentence}
Dialogue: 10,0:13:20.03,0:13:22.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Why is it that Fujimaki gets to go on a date...
Dialogue: 10,0:13:22.90,0:13:24.47,Default,,0,0,0,,And we're digging potatoes?!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:25.06,0:13:29.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Don’t you think it’s good for everyone to reconnect with nature once in a while?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:29.88,0:13:31.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:31.71,0:13:35.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't sign up to dig up potatoes \Nfor the sake of another's happiness. {no clue}
Dialogue: 10,0:13:35.44,0:13:36.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm so pissed off!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:36.61,0:13:38.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Reiko-sama...!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:38.55,0:13:40.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Now! Why don't you just shut up and dig!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:47.06,0:13:51.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, look! People and cars look so small!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:51.43,0:13:52.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh? Yeah...
Dialogue: 10,0:13:52.55,0:13:55.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, let's ride that next, okay?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:55.75,0:13:57.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-Yeah...
Dialogue: 10,0:13:58.43,0:14:01.27,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong? Are you unwell?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:01.27,0:14:03.37,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not that...
Dialogue: 10,0:14:03.37,0:14:03.94,Default,,0,0,0,,But what?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:03.94,0:14:07.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Um... Why did you invite me?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:08.28,0:14:11.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Captain or Uchida-senpai would've made more sense.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:11.28,0:14:13.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, it's just that...
Dialogue: 10,0:14:13.88,0:14:15.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you dislike me?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:15.28,0:14:16.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:16.08,0:14:18.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Wouldn’t anyone besides Mariko-chan work?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:18.25,0:14:21.32,Default,,0,0,0,,What if it was Coach Misaki? \NOr her Grandma?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:21.32,0:14:23.55,Default,,0,0,0,,N-No... Of course not.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:24.09,0:14:26.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's enjoy ourselves today, then!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:26.13,0:14:27.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay? Okay?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:28.33,0:14:29.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:31.43,0:14:35.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow... I haven't been \Non a roller coaster since I was a kid!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:35.87,0:14:36.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I see...
Dialogue: 10,0:14:36.39,0:14:40.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you afraid of this kind of thing, Shun-kun? {lit: fine with it}
Dialogue: 10,0:14:40.54,0:14:42.01,Default,,0,0,0,,No, not much.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:42.01,0:14:45.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I see... Well, actually, I really can't...
Dialogue: 10,0:14:45.60,0:14:49.05,Default,,0,0,0,,stand this kind of thing! {lit: bad at it}
Dialogue: 10,0:15:01.43,0:15:04.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen up, whoever draws the longest one wins.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:04.50,0:15:05.10,Default,,0,0,0,,All right...
Dialogue: 10,0:15:05.10,0:15:05.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's do it!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:05.79,0:15:06.57,Default,,0,0,0,,This is...
Dialogue: 10,0:15:06.57,0:15:07.46,Default,,0,0,0,,My victory...
Dialogue: 10,0:15:07.46,0:15:09.36,Default,,0,0,0,,With the last one! {no clue: blow on the remaining one}
Dialogue: 10,0:15:09.97,0:15:11.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Which one?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:11.29,0:15:13.53,Default,,0,0,0,,It's mine! Mine is the longest!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:13.57,0:15:16.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Whatdja say?! \NIt's obviously mine!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:16.00,0:15:18.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Counting with the root, it's my victory!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:18.38,0:15:19.58,Default,,0,0,0,,What was that?! {nc}
Dialogue: 10,0:15:19.58,0:15:20.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you stupid?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:20.38,0:15:21.18,Default,,0,0,0,,It's me!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:21.18,0:15:22.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Mine's the longest!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:22.75,0:15:24.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{w/e}
Dialogue: 10,0:15:24.52,0:15:26.12,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:26.12,0:15:29.62,Default,,0,0,0,,It seems they're competing \Nfor who gets to be in a slump next.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:29.62,0:15:32.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Because then that person will get to go on a date with Reiko-senpai.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:32.96,0:15:34.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Blithering fools!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:42.54,0:15:45.14,Default,,0,0,0,,What should we ride next \Nafter we finish this?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:45.14,0:15:48.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I like going around in circles, so maybe... Hey!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:49.48,0:15:50.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Shun-kun?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:08.26,0:16:09.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Shun-kun?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:14.44,0:16:15.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Shun-kun!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:18.86,0:16:20.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh no...
Dialogue: 10,0:16:20.02,0:16:21.63,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the matter, Shun-kun?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:21.63,0:16:22.98,Default,,0,0,0,,N-No, it's just...
Dialogue: 10,0:16:26.02,0:16:27.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Shun-kun...
Dialogue: 10,0:16:31.61,0:16:34.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Shun-kun, thank you for joining me today.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:34.72,0:16:36.02,Default,,0,0,0,,It was my pleasure.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:36.02,0:16:37.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, see you tomorrow.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:38.92,0:16:40.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Reiko-senpai.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:41.66,0:16:44.53,Default,,0,0,0,,N-No, it's nothing.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:44.53,0:16:47.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much for today.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:49.60,0:16:50.77,Thought,,0,0,0,,Shun-kun...
Dialogue: 10,0:16:53.60,0:16:58.35,Default,,0,0,0,,If only Fujimaki could let go of the bar in the first place, none of this would have happened!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:58.35,0:17:02.54,Default,,0,0,0,,So there's no moving forward until we cure him. \NMaybe send him on another date?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:02.54,0:17:05.59,Default,,0,0,0,,How about we cover the bar in oil?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:05.59,0:17:09.06,Default,,0,0,0,,That means he wouldn't be able to grab it, \Nand we need him to let go!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:09.06,0:17:11.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Attach a rope to his hands \Nand yank him off it!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:11.43,0:17:13.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Then who's gonna catch him? {no clue what's this foro/foru}
Dialogue: 10,0:17:15.50,0:17:16.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Um...
Dialogue: 10,0:17:17.12,0:17:20.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Couldn't we pass a current through the bar?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:20.37,0:17:22.20,Default,,0,0,0,,What? Electric current?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:22.20,0:17:26.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Time it right and turn on the current—\Nhe’ll fly off instantly. {/get electrified}
Dialogue: 10,0:17:26.71,0:17:30.71,Default,,0,0,0,,O-On second thought, forget it. \NIt's too dangerous.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:30.71,0:17:33.52,Default,,0,0,0,,What a stupid idea. \NWe're not in some cartoon, you know.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:34.18,0:17:37.79,Default,,0,0,0,,No, let's pass the current through. \NIt has to do!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:38.52,0:17:39.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Captain?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:39.92,0:17:42.96,Default,,0,0,0,,D-Don't be ridiculous. \NPlease think about it.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:42.96,0:17:44.71,Default,,0,0,0,,We want to heal him, not kill him! {lit: if he dies from electrocution, it'd be unbearable}
Dialogue: 10,0:17:44.71,0:17:46.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Just a small battery would suffice.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:46.85,0:17:49.36,Default,,0,0,0,,We only need him partly paralyzed. {lit: if he's a little numb that's enough - trying to make it sound more menacing}
Dialogue: 10,0:17:49.36,0:17:51.10,Default,,0,0,0,,We can do it with electricity!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:51.10,0:17:52.50,Default,,0,0,0,,R-Right...
Dialogue: 10,0:17:53.02,0:17:54.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's get to designing it at once!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:54.56,0:17:58.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I name it {\i1}Operation Ultra Gamba Part 3!{\i0}
Dialogue: 10,0:17:58.26,0:17:59.77,Default,,0,0,0,,C-Captain?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:59.77,0:18:04.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Uchida will procure the battery, Higashi—cords. Sanada, you take care of the switches!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:04.38,0:18:06.58,Default,,0,0,0,,O-Okay, got it...
Dialogue: 10,0:18:06.58,0:18:08.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-Yeah...
Dialogue: 10,0:18:10.44,0:18:13.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello? My name is Orikasa. \NCan I talk to Shun?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:13.54,0:18:16.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? He hadn't come home yet?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:20.93,0:18:22.16,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no way...
Dialogue: 10,0:18:25.29,0:18:26.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Shun-kun!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:37.83,0:18:39.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Shun-kun!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:49.09,0:18:51.93,Default,,0,0,0,,R-Reiko-senpai...
Dialogue: 10,0:18:54.20,0:18:57.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I just can't do it... \NNo matter what I do!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:00.57,0:19:01.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Enough already...
Dialogue: 10,0:19:04.47,0:19:06.17,Default,,0,0,0,,That's enough!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:07.74,0:19:09.38,Default,,0,0,0,,You shouldn't do that...
Dialogue: 10,0:19:10.75,0:19:13.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll stain your shirt...
Dialogue: 10,0:19:17.64,0:19:21.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh my? Did we leave our gate wide open?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:21.36,0:19:23.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure I closed it.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:23.79,0:19:24.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Unless...
Dialogue: 10,0:19:34.22,0:19:37.20,Default,,0,0,0,,That was so irresponsible of you, young man!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:37.20,0:19:40.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I'll walk Orikasa home, then.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:40.47,0:19:42.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. Thank you.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:42.11,0:19:43.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Good night.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:44.24,0:19:47.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Shun, you should stay the night.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:04.33,0:20:05.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Who could it be?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:06.77,0:20:08.44,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not a thief, is it?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:11.14,0:20:12.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-What's this?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:13.37,0:20:15.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Why is he here?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:15.78,0:20:17.65,Default,,0,0,0,,He's not dead, is he?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:19.55,0:20:21.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Dobriy den'!{\i0} {/G'day! - it's not really day, it's night}
Dialogue: 10,0:20:24.49,0:20:26.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Dobriy den'...{\i0}
Dialogue: 10,0:20:25.44,0:20:26.81,Overlap,,0,0,0,,Oh no, it's a foreigner! {no clue}
Dialogue: 10,0:20:28.96,0:20:30.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Dobriy den'!{\i0}
Dialogue: 10,0:20:30.46,0:20:33.56,Default,,0,0,0,,That's how you say "Hello" in Russian! {/Good Morning}
Dialogue: 10,0:20:33.56,0:20:35.05,Default,,0,0,0,,R-Russian?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:35.05,0:20:37.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm? What's with your hands?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:37.83,0:20:40.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, I... I got in on the high bar...
Dialogue: 10,0:20:40.72,0:20:43.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Boy... Do you like the high bar?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:43.96,0:20:47.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I do like it... I suppose.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:47.43,0:20:50.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you here in the middle of the night?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:50.40,0:20:56.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow! Seiji’s mom! \NI’ve dreamed of meeting you for ages!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:56.11,0:20:58.55,Default,,0,0,0,,What's this sudden outburst of love?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:59.19,0:21:01.48,Default,,0,0,0,,What happened to his hand?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:01.48,0:21:05.60,Default,,0,0,0,,You see, he doesn't seem to be able \Nto let go of the high bar.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:05.60,0:21:07.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Can't let go?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:07.05,0:21:12.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh! That disease is very easy to cure! \NI can do it with a single stroke! {no clue what he means by ippatsu, maybe a reference to "one cup of vodka"}
Dialogue: 10,0:21:13.37,0:21:14.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Single stroke?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:14.76,0:21:16.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:17.14,0:21:18.91,Default,,0,0,0,,A single stroke, sir!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:19.71,0:21:21.73,Default,,0,0,0,,D-Don't tell me you're...
Dialogue: 10,0:21:22.61,0:21:25.15,Default,,0,0,0,,The former world champion?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:25.61,0:21:28.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, Sergei Andrianov here.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:28.87,0:21:32.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Th-The world champion?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:33.10,0:21:35.06,Narrator,,0,0,0,,There's no way it's true, right?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:35.06,0:21:38.96,Narrator,,0,0,0,,How could this suspicious foreigner \Nbe the world champion, right?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:38.96,0:21:45.03,Narrator,,0,0,0,,But when he says he can cured you with a single stroke, what are you going to do, Ganbarist Shun?
Dialogue: 10,0:23:16.02,0:23:17.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I came to return this.
Dialogue: 10,0:23:17.89,0:23:20.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Japan's national team uniform?
Dialogue: 10,0:23:20.95,0:23:22.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Is this...
Dialogue: 10,0:23:23.30,0:23:25.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Seiji's uniform?
Dialogue: 10,0:23:26.27,0:23:28.29,Default,,0,0,0,,At the world championship,
Dialogue: 10,0:23:28.29,0:23:33.26,Default,,0,0,0,,when I first met Seiji-san, \Nhe gifted me this uniform.
Dialogue: 10,0:23:33.84,0:23:36.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Seiji was a truly wonderful athlete.
Dialogue: 10,0:23:36.78,0:23:40.01,Default,,0,0,0,,So this uniform became my talisman.
Dialogue: 10,0:23:40.01,0:23:45.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Next Ganba: A Revival! \NThe First Step Towards New Hope. {復活だ!新たな希望の第一歩}
Dialogue: 10,0:23:45.01,0:23:47.20,NarratorTop,,0,0,0,,Today it's finally the backflip.
Dialogue: 10,0:23:47.20,0:23:50.28,NarratorTop,,0,0,0,,The first point is, if someone is afraid of jumping backwards,
Dialogue: 10,0:23:50.28,0:23:51.91,NarratorTop,,0,0,0,,hold their hands firmly
Dialogue: 10,0:23:51.91,0:23:53.69,NarratorTop,,0,0,0,,throw them over yourself.
Dialogue: 10,0:23:54.68,0:23:57.66,NarratorTop,,0,0,0,,The second point is, swing your hands strongly and jump backwards.
Dialogue: 10,0:23:57.66,0:23:59.99,NarratorTop,,0,0,0,,At first, always have someone support you.
